<li id="cite_note-boehm2004-13">^ <a href="#cite_ref-boehm2004_13-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-boehm2004_13-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-boehm2004_13-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFBoehm.5B.5BRichard_Turner_.28software.29.7CR._Turner.5D.5D2004"><a href="/wiki/Barry_Boehm" title="Barry Boehm">Boehm, B.</a>; <a href="/wiki/Richard_Turner_(software)" title="Richard Turner (software)">R. Turner</a> (2004). <i>Balancing Agility and Discipline: A Guide for the Perplexed</i>. Boston, MA: Addison-Wesley. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0321186125" class="internal">ISBN 0-321-18612-5</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Balancing+Agility+and+Discipline%3A+A+Guide+for+the+Perplexed&amp;rft.aulast=Boehm&amp;rft.aufirst=B.&amp;rft.au=Boehm%2C+B.&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BRichard+Turner+%28software%29%7CR.+Turner%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.place=Boston%2C+MA&amp;rft.pub=Addison-Wesley&amp;rft.isbn=0-321-18612-5&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Agile_software_development"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
